flowchart TD
    %% Brownfield Flow — archaeology before bootstrap

    CODE[(Existing Codebase<br/>code + tests + history)] --> INIT[brownfield-init<br/>read-only archaeology sweep]

    INIT --> MAP[Brownfield Map<br/>risky paths + implicit contracts]
    INIT --> GRAPH[Dependency Graph<br/>fan-in / blast radius]
    INIT --> HEUR[Seed heuristics<br/>with file-backed watchouts]

    MAP --> START[starter-init<br/>bootstrap harness after archaeology]
    GRAPH --> START
    HEUR --> START

    START --> READ[Read brownfield map<br/>manually when planning work]
    READ --> SPEC[spec-requirements<br/>Current Context section<br/>brownfield risk rating]
    SPEC --> SAFE([Pick smallest safe<br/>first-touch surface])
    SAFE --> LOOP([Standard per-feature loop<br/>spec to verify])

    NOTE[Router caveat:<br/>brownfield artifacts live in memories/repo/brownfield/<br/>but are not auto-loaded by INDEX.md yet]
    NOTE -.-> READ

    classDef terminal fill:#0d0d0d,stroke:#0d0d0d,color:#fff
    classDef brown fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#b45309,color:#fff
    classDef step fill:#fff,stroke:#d0d7de,color:#0d0d0d
    classDef preserve fill:#fcf3f3,stroke:#f2c4c4,color:#c62828

    class CODE,SAFE,LOOP terminal
    class INIT,MAP,GRAPH,HEUR,START,SPEC brown
    class READ step
    class NOTE preserve
